Package cz.vse.java.utils.xml

Class ListOfNodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.vse.java.utils.xml.ListOfNodes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<org.w3c.dom.Node>, org.w3c.dom.NodeList
    public class ListOfNodes
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.w3c.dom.NodeList, java.lang.Iterable<org.w3c.dom.Node>

    The class of ListOfNodes is used to abstractly define the type of the instances.

    This class contains methods for dealing with a List of Nodes (in W3C XML context). Substitutes basic NodeList, where there is no possibility to iterate through and eliminates empty text nodes (made out of whitespaces)

    Written for project "Utils".
    Version:
    13. 02. 2020
    Author:
    Vojtěch Pavlů
